Code preview of the table CON_合同条款付款信息

drop table "CON_TermPayment" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_TermPayment" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_TermPayment"
(
"TermPaymentID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TermType" INTEGER not null,
"TermName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"TermCode" VARCHAR2(10),
"AccountKey" VARCHAR2(10),
"TaxType" VARCHAR2(10) default 'MWST' not null,
"TaxGroup" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"IsGross" VARCHAR2(10),
"BPCode" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"ChangeIndicator" CHAR(1) default 'N' not null,
"SyncSAPflag" INTEGER default 0 not null,
constraint PK_CON_TERMPAYMENT primary key ("TermPaymentID")
);

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."TermType" is
'1:合同租金 2:审批优惠
';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."TermName" is
'对应SAP的TERM_TEXT';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."TermCode" is
'对应SAP的TERM_NO
默认空
有0010,0020等';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."AccountKey" is
'对应SAP的ACC_DET_KEY
如属于合并范围内关联方，设置为Z001，否则为空';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."TaxType" is
'对应SAP的TAX_TYPE
默认值MWST';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."TaxGroup" is
'对应SAP的TAX_GROUP
必输，依据实际需要设置为NONE或YYS或ZZS';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."IsGross" is
'对应SAP的IS_GROSS
默认为空，如选择ZZS，则必选，否则为空';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."BPCode" is
'必输，输入角色为Z001对应的承租方编码';

comment on column "CON_TermPayment"."ChangeIndicator" is
'N:初始创建
I:新增
D:删除';
